.prelim 'Preface'
.pp
This manual reflects the standards selected by Rockwell International
for the maintenance of Source distributed software packages.  In
specific this manual is designed for the Job Entry Subsystem 3 product
of IBM.  The intent is that all source changes to JES3
.us will
be maintained using the IBM product System Modification Program (SMP 4).
SMP/E will be addressed in a future release of this document.
.pp
This manual was developed to provide standards for source development
for JES3. BUT the primary intent was to overcome some of the problems
with using SMP to maintain source.  There are still many problems since
SMP basically handles source in the same way it handles object decks.
With the difference being that SMP does recognize incremental updates
for source type elements.  What is not handled at all is the ability
to RESTORE selected source updates without having to RESTORE all
non-ACCEPTED maintenance.  In this manual a technique is suggested to
simplify these problems.
.sp 2
.pp
